{"tid":1689254,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人應該要做嘅係每個人都帶報紙上街","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:22:34.000Z","uid":151057,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f67622ac6e922d5a446334336684eefd18479e6b","tid":1689254,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:27:15.000Z","msg":"將報紙卷起 再對摺 然後捆一圈膠紙<br />\n<br />\n當每個人手上有報紙棒<br />\n先會開始記起自己要反抗<br />\n<br />\n十萬人十萬人枝報紙棒<br />\n有人唔記得帶報紙就捲畀佢<br />\n當集體擁有一種象徵同埋道具<br />\n香港人唔會再俾人覺得軟弱無能"},{"pid":"5eea157d6aa13962ccbedd648214f24c1216e8e3","tid":1689254,"uid":117265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"有遮都唔用，仲講報紙棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d14c6b2d0283d69959f8ddf2a79c4bccd45a6e5","tid":1689254,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"e135291ce24397491f4c4a055894ea7cdd0b29c6","tid":1689254,"uid":151057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5eea157d6aa13962ccbedd648214f24c1216e8e3","tid":1689254,"uid":117265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:29:16.000Z","msg":"有遮都唔用，仲講報紙棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/